{"tid":942467,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"莫迪歷轟「C斯」缺席金球獎","createTime":"2018-12-15T17:38:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-16T03:24:57.000Z","uid":132262,"like":3,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"97af2d8dbeccdc5b807bc3d53f8af81f82d2f1b3","tid":942467,"uid":132262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T17:38:15.000Z","msg":"莫迪歷轟「C斯」缺席金球獎<br />\n<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=f%2F%2FW%2BDv6GxMhMlVYbxGAZsmDuOf2Rd%2FwnGcLKIjXoko%3D&h=edca48e8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a> 體育<br />\n<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=f%2F%2FW%2BDv6GxMhMlVYbxGAZsmDuOf2Rd%2FwnGcLKIjXoko%3D&h=edca48e8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a> 體育2018年12月15日 下午3:17 [GMT]<br />\n【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=f%2F%2FW%2BDv6GxMhMlVYbxGAZsmDuOf2Rd%2FwnGcLKIjXoko%3D&h=edca48e8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】基斯坦奴朗拿度、美斯缺席早前的金球獎頒獎禮，得主莫迪歷炮轟2人不尊重。<br />\n<br />\n先後帶領皇家馬德里達成歐聯3連霸、助克羅地亞國家隊成為世界盃亞軍，中場莫迪歷（Luka Modric）大熱當選金球獎，打破了基斯坦奴朗拿度、美斯的10年壟斷。 由於得獎機會低，C朗及美斯皆缺席頒獎禮，莫迪歷對此表示：「不合理。原來只有他們勝出，這些獎項才有價值。這對他們的隊友，以及過去10年投他們票的人很不公平。不過我重申，每個人都有權做他們覺得認為要做的事。」 今夏盛傳莫迪歷會加盟國際米蘭，但最終留在皇馬，他坦言：「佩雷斯告訴我『放棄離隊的念頭吧，我們不會賣走你』，所以我將會完成合約，即是留下來直至2020年。」"},{"pid":"9cd5a9322972ab6f1c352c9b2538669d0ed9dcc4","tid":942467,"uid":46925,"like":51,"dislike":8,"score":43,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T17:40:28.000Z","msg":"你咁廢都有 唔缺席抗議下咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"838c89a1a15901f20de3846f787dfaf85a880333","tid":942467,"uid":72334,"like":37,"dislike":5,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T19:38:33.000Z","msg":"我係你就靜啦 俾你拎仲要抽水<br />\n你唔係真係咁值架咋 仲有資格話人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呀朗仲要係你前隊友"},{"pid":"3920b50ad53ad9ff307f2709069316dcd94e98ee","tid":942467,"uid":12169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0